Package: HLAinTCGA
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of HLA Allele and Genotype Frequencies Across TCGA Projects
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Shahram Aliyari
Maintainer: Shahram Aliyari <your_email@example.com>
Description: 
    HLAinTCGA provides functions to analyze and visualize the frequencies of HLA alleles and genotypes across various TCGA projects.
    The package includes tools for stratification by demographic and clinical categories such as ethnicity, gender, race, and disease stage.
    It offers flexible and interactive visualizations to aid research on allele distributions and their expression levels.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
